<h2>CLR - <u>C</u>ommon <u>L</u>anguage <u>R</u>untime</h2>

<ul>
    <li><font size="4">Manages common runtime tasks</font><ul>
            <li><font size="4">Memory management</font></li>
            <li><font size="4">Process/thread scheduling and
                control</font></li>
            <li><font size="4">Execution security policies</font></li>
            <li><font size="4">Dependencies between components</font></li>
        </ul>
    </li>
    <li><font size="4">Unified environment that can work across
        many programming languages</font></li>
</ul>

<h2>Unified Programming Classes</h2>

<ul>
    <li><font size="4">Provides common set of GUI widgets and
        other &quot;common&quot; utility classes to replace
        disparate libraries</font><ul>
            <li><font size="4">MFC</font></li>
            <li><font size="4">WFC</font></li>
            <li><font size="4">VB</font></li>
        </ul>
    </li>
</ul>

<h2>ASP+</h2>

<ul>
    <li><font size="4">Builds on the unified programming classes
        to provide web applications UI widgets and control
        infrastructure</font></li>
</ul>

